Save the date 30-31st Jan 2021  Tune in for more details&hellip;

The book &ldquo;Agile IT Organization Design - For digital transformation and continuous delivery&rdquo; by Sriram Narayan explains software development as a design process. Following statement from the book means a lot.
 &ldquo;Software development is a design process, and the production environment is the factory where product takes place. IT OPS work to keep the factory running..&rdquo;
 It questions the way we traditionally think of operation support, maintenance, production bugs, rework, their costs and budgets and the focus in software development life.
